Axios v1 encodes nested objects in [qs style](https://www.npmjs.com/package/qs), not as JSON string.
Unfortunately qs [does not support](https://github.com/ljharb/qs/issues/362) serializing a nested object with an empty structure and there is no specification for this or well-known practice.

```js
